            <div type="edition" xml:space="preserve"><head>Text</head><ab><lb n="1"/>
                Mercurio <lb n="2"/><expan><abbr>Arvernorig</abbr><ex>i</ex></expan> <lb n="3"/>Cossillus d<lb break="no" n="4"/>onavi <note>sic</note> es <note>sic</note> visu <lb n="5"/>l<expan><ex>a</ex><abbr>etus</abbr></expan> libe<expan><ex>n</ex><abbr>s</abbr></expan> meri<lb break="no" n="6"/>to
            </ab></div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>Drei Fragmente eines einteiligen Altars für Mercurius Arvernorix. (B): Z. 2: Arvernoric[i]. Weniger wahrscheinlich: Z. 3/4: Beckmann: Donavi (filius). Autopsie R. Wiegels.</p>
            </div>
